gg : 1line

WINDOWS
ctrl+w s : split horizontal
ctrl+w v : split vertical
ctrl+w w : change next window
ctrl+w hjkl : change window

MOVE
w : next word 1rst letter
b : previous word 1rst letter
e : end of word
0 : first of line
^ : first non blank char
$ : end of line
G2 : go to line 2

INSERT
ea : insert after word

VISUAL
v : enter visual mode
V : enter visual mode +(select current line)
